      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "10.  Imam Musa Kadhim (a.s.) was asked, “Is it better for a rich person to give  Sadaqah or  to buy  a  slave  and  free  him?” Imam (a.s.) replied, “I prefer Sadaqah.”"
